data.description: ***Assumable loan at $4.625%!*** Come see this stunning 4 Bed/3 Bath Sandy Home with breathtaking views! Nestled in the coveted east bench neighborhood, this remarkable residence offers an exceptional blend of modern comfort and scenic beauty. This home provides an inviting space for families and individuals alike. You will love the views from inside the house, as well as from the porch and back deck. This home boasts a new roof, new AC & Furnace, as well as a new deck and stairs, ensuring worry-free living and a stylish outdoor space for relaxation and entertainment. The updated kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting sleek countertops, modern appliances, and ample storage, making meal preparation a true pleasure. With its perfect blend of modern upgrades, unbeatable location, and mesmerizing views, this home is truly a gem that offers the best of both worlds. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own. Check out the 3D Tour and schedule your showing today!   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from appraisal. Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
